{"tid":1919112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"進攻冇可能贏嘅功能組別 放被DQ獅入去 然後DQ番啲保皇黨","createTime":"2020-03-10T14:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T08:12:06.000Z","uid":210495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8b89e8ce362461f1c2284489e3045a4179dd2f18","tid":1919112,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"今次呢個post個重點係：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點冇可能贏嘅功能組別</span></span></strong><br />\n呢個建議之前唔知邊個post嘅巴打提過<br />\n我覺得係相當可行<br />\n與其叫gif去九龍東然後plan B 梁凱晴 (suppose佢真係會比人DQ)<br />\n不如去一d實輸嘅功能組別<br />\n例如係 漁農界 保險界 航運交通界 勞工界 旅遊界 商界（二）工業界（一）<br />\n工業界（二） 金融界 金融服務界<br />\n不過前提係 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要夠提名</span></span></strong><br />\n上屆保險界陳健波大獵7成選民提名<br />\n<br />\n當一選完就呈請 呈請完法官就會判非妥為當選<br />\n然後<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">保皇黨就會少一席</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"47c28ae332461fec8b4ee6f9c1a01e1c23bd68e3","tid":1919112,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:28:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47eda2215588edb2210669536e1681d41aac5bbf","tid":1919112,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"放d比人dq過既友入去<br />\n就精彩<br />\n我唔關心選成點<br />\n最緊要係有咩後續係對港共不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a9d2398de543fd217a5e2904928106c9bfdbd9","tid":1919112,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c44974a2fa85d44290eb43e244f702fbf6a8f61b","tid":1919112,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:33:29.000Z","msg":"呈請其實未必贏<br />\n不過呢個諗法唔錯"},{"pid":"f07d04e23e22b27a664e09c6eaa201d5cde405a8","tid":1919112,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"好橋 陳浩天考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbe2e6a2ddcafc22f5471fa3aa530d20052b18c","tid":1919112,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"有俾機會回應係可以DQ"},{"pid":"ae544484d0811a29838cfcb3606588d755c90a86","tid":1919112,"uid":195690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:40:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6669113840344b803f6ca28a61691da46918ff34","tid":1919112,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"參選功能界別要「與該功能界別有密切聯繫」"},{"pid":"d6bd5335c776ec3b56c8ebd0c90e02f829c24b60","tid":1919112,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6669113840344b803f6ca28a61691da46918ff34","tid":1919112,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"參選功能界別要「與該功能界別有密切聯繫」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:49:50.000Z","msg":"《立法會條例》第3（2）（b）條已就某人與某功能界別有「密切聯繫」的情況作闡釋，即包括（但不限於）為該功能界別的團體選民的成員、會員、合夥人、僱員或（如該團體是法人團體）高級人員或（如該團體不是法人團體）人員，或為該團體選民的團體成員；或屬於指明為該功能界別的選民的某類別人士。<br />\n<br />\n  至於參選人是否與有關功能界別有密切聯繫，須視乎每一個案的實際情況而定。根據《立法會條例》第42A條和《選舉管理委員會（選舉程序）（立法會）規例》（第541D章）第16條，參選人的提名是否有效，由選舉主任按照法例的要求及相關程序作出決定。視乎每宗個案的實際情況，選舉主任會諮詢提名顧問委員會的法律意見，並在有需要時要求參選人提供其認為適當的額外資料，以令其信納參選人有資格獲提名或該項提名是有效的。選舉主任會按相關法例和相關資料，就參選人的提名是否有效作出決定。"},{"pid":"758384bf0d96ad88711393d8a6a9be3717385cb4","tid":1919112,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cbe2e6a2ddcafc22f5471fa3aa530d20052b18c","tid":1919112,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"有俾機會回應係可以DQ"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"就係要佢DQ <br />\n然後呈請"},{"pid":"b8c801cffa1c38b36adb11fcd79b6b3f18e866c5","tid":1919112,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:12:06.000Z","msg":"用心制作，請用5 分鐘了解功能組別登記<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p59mZyffEao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp59mZyffEao&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=3e076892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p59mZyffEao</a>"}]}